Top Stories (December 12)

CALPINE PLANT - 2: TO OPERATE IN JUNE 2004 IF APPROVED
Calpine Corp. is considering building a $550 million, 1,100-megawatt electric 
generating plant to power one million homes in northern California.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2000/
12/12/eng-djn/eng-djn_152023_108_913150113076

'KILOWATT DIVIDE' SEPARATES WINNERS, LOSERS IN CALIFORNIA ENERGY CRISIS
There were fresh signs Monday that California's flawed electricity market is 
dividing the state's power players into winners and losers.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMAKRT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/knightri
dder/2000/12/12/krtbn/0000-0285-OC-ENERGY-CRISIS

MIDWEST GRID OPERATOR MUST MERGE OR EXPAND TO SURVIVE - CEO
The Midwest Independent System Operator Inc., wracked by three significant 
defections, must either expand or reach an agreement to combine with its main 
competitor if it is to remain viable, the emerging grid operator's chief 
executive said Tuesday.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2000/
12/12/eng-djn/eng-djn_164024_196_066375742666

US ENERGY SECRETARY WARNS POWER PRODUCERS IN WEST ON PRICES
As California's electricity system teeters on the brink of collapse, U.S. 
Energy Secretary Bill Richardson warned power producers not to attempt to 
take advantage of the power-supply crisis.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2000/
12/12/eng-djn/eng-djn_170027_216_596333063208

NIAGARA MOWHAWK, NYSEG, ROCHESTER GAS & ELECTRIC AND CENTRAL HUDSON TO SELL 
NINE MILE POINT NUCLEAR ASSETS IN DEAL VALUED AT $1.04 BILLION
Niagara Mohawk Power Corp. will sell its ownership of the Nine Mile Point 1 
and 2 nuclear plants, and New York State Electric & Gas Corp., Rochester Gas 
and Electric Corp., and Central Hudson Gas & Electric Corp. have agreed to 
sell their ownership of the Nine Mile 2 nuclear plant, to Constellation 
Nuclear, under an agreement announced today.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMANAT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/comtex/2
000/12/12/pr/0000-0884-ny-niagaramohawk9mile

